# ovh_vps_backup_ftp (Data Source)

Use this data source to retrieve information about the FTP backup storage for an OVHcloud VPS.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/vps_backup_ftp/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/data-sources/vps_backup_ftp.md for the full attribute list.)

* `id` - The ID of the FTP backup.
* `ftp_backup_name` - The FTP backup service name.
* `login` - FTP login.
* `quota_size` - Quota size in GB.
* `quota_used` - Quota used in GB.
* `state` - State of the FTP backup.
* `type` - Type of the FTP backup.
* `url` - URL for FTP access.
